1
00:00:00,918 --> 00:00:06,500
In this prison, when they caught me the first time

2
00:00:06,626 --> 00:00:10,250
He first flogged me 10 lashes

3
00:00:11,876 --> 00:00:14,500
I was blindfolded, then he put me in prison

4
00:00:15,751 --> 00:00:19,167
Then after three days he took me out and flogged me again

5
00:00:20,667 --> 00:00:24,876
Then they put me back in prison, and three days later they took me out

6
00:00:26,584 --> 00:00:29,626
The second time, when they brought me

7
00:00:30,834 --> 00:00:32,709
He put me in that house I told you about

8
00:00:32,709 --> 00:00:34,083
Then they brought me back to prison

9
00:00:34,834 --> 00:00:38,834
And also on the first day he flogged me and put me in prison

10
00:00:40,959 --> 00:00:43,292
Then I was flogged again

11
00:00:45,125 --> 00:00:46,500
And after that I was flogged again

12
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:51,667
I was flogged five times in this prison, five times

13
00:00:52,334 --> 00:00:55,751
Every time they flogged me 10 lashes

14
00:00:58,334 --> 00:01:04,042
Imagine that when I came out my back was all marked with lines

15
00:01:05,959 --> 00:01:07,334
Like zebra stripes

16
00:01:10,918 --> 00:01:13,959
Blue, red, and green because of the heavy beating

17
00:01:14,584 --> 00:01:18,250
Because he doesn’t hit you lightly

18
00:01:19,125 --> 00:01:23,209
He flogs you hard, until he makes you scream

19
00:01:23,626 --> 00:01:26,417
And because I didn’t scream, he increased the beating

20
00:01:29,292 --> 00:01:33,417
Interviewer: Did he want certain information from you while flogging you?

21
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,459
He asked me why I’d been brought in

22
00:01:40,334 --> 00:01:43,584
Because maybe the one flogging me didn’t know the reason

23
00:01:45,459 --> 00:01:47,709
That was my theory

24
00:01:48,042 --> 00:01:50,792
Because he would ask me, Why am I flogging you?

25
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:53,042
And I would say, Because of cigarettes

26
00:01:56,584 --> 00:01:57,792
Then he would flog me

27
00:01:58,125 --> 00:02:00,042
He asked me, Do you smoke cigarettes? I said, Yes

28
00:02:00,792 --> 00:02:03,417
Then he flogged me, then he asked, When you get out will you smoke again?

29
00:02:04,042 --> 00:02:06,000
I said, No, I will quit, then he said, You’re lying

30
00:02:06,292 --> 00:02:08,417
Then he flogged me, that’s how it was

31
00:02:09,167 --> 00:02:11,083
If you told him you’d quit, he wouldn’t believe you

32
00:02:11,959 --> 00:02:14,876
Even if you swore to God you’d quit, he wouldn’t believe you

33
00:02:21,584 --> 00:02:28,709
Interviewer: What were the types of torture used inside the prison?

34
00:02:29,083 --> 00:02:31,334
Especially while you were there

35
00:02:31,584 --> 00:02:34,792
I mean what was the torture you saw with your own eyes?

36
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,209
Witness: With my own eyes?

37
00:02:38,876 --> 00:02:44,792
Interviewer: Not with your eyes, I mean how were the prisoners with you tortured?

38
00:02:45,834 --> 00:02:47,042
I mean the ones you heard

39
00:02:47,417 --> 00:02:49,083
Because no one could see it directly

40
00:02:49,125 --> 00:02:52,125
Even when they flogged you, they blindfolded you

41
00:02:53,083 --> 00:02:54,876
So you couldn’t see in front of you

42
00:02:55,751 --> 00:02:57,834
When they took you out they blindfolded you

43
00:02:58,250 --> 00:03:01,709
They took you to a room, flogged you, talked to you, then brought you back

44
00:03:02,876 --> 00:03:07,709
As for the torture used, it was flogging

45
00:03:10,125 --> 00:03:12,292
We didn’t see other types of torture

46
00:03:12,959 --> 00:03:15,542
No one saw the torture of others

47
00:03:16,250 --> 00:03:20,375
Many people, when they came out, they talked

48
00:03:20,751 --> 00:03:24,709
One said, They hung me, another said, They tied me to the wall

49
00:03:25,417 --> 00:03:29,792
So there were many forms of torture

50
00:03:33,792 --> 00:03:38,083
Interviewer: Did they make you do cleaning work inside the prison?

51
00:03:38,584 --> 00:03:40,000
Yes, they made us work

52
00:03:40,375 --> 00:03:45,834
Interviewer: How?
Witness: One of them came in and looked around like this

53
00:03:45,834 --> 00:03:48,125
And said, You, sweep here

54
00:03:48,375 --> 00:03:49,792
And you, clean the toilet

55
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:54,083
And you, wash this place

56
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:56,918
And you, wipe and clean the wall

57
00:03:58,542 --> 00:04:02,334
It’s a prison, they don’t bring one of their own to clean

58
00:04:06,334 --> 00:04:09,667
Interviewer: Did they use certain tools or means for torture?

59
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:13,334
Do you mean instruments?

60
00:04:13,334 --> 00:04:16,042
Interviewer: Like beating on the feet, or kicking

61
00:04:16,459 --> 00:04:19,042
I mean hitting you with their shoes

62
00:04:19,083 --> 00:04:24,792
Yes, for me they didn’t kick me or anything like that

63
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:29,751
But they beat others, that happened during interrogation

64
00:04:30,876 --> 00:04:32,459
While interrogating, he would hit him

65
00:04:34,417 --> 00:04:38,334
So there were people beaten during interrogation

66
00:04:41,375 --> 00:04:44,083
But I didn’t know who was being beaten

67
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:50,959
Because when we heard the sounds of torture

68
00:04:51,751 --> 00:04:53,459
That meant someone was being tortured

69
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:57,042
Maybe they tortured him then took him somewhere else

70
00:04:58,083 --> 00:05:00,459
We didn’t know, maybe not only in this prison

71
00:05:00,918 --> 00:05:02,751
There might have been another prison

72
00:05:07,375 --> 00:05:09,542
Interviewer: Did they curse during torture?

73
00:05:10,709 --> 00:05:12,792
Me, I didn’t hear that

74
00:05:14,042 --> 00:05:15,542
I didn’t hear them cursing

75
00:05:18,584 --> 00:05:20,334
And they didn’t curse me either

76
00:05:23,792 --> 00:05:26,459
They brought a boy and imprisoned him with us

77
00:05:27,167 --> 00:05:29,125
We didn’t know what his charge was

78
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:35,626
Even in prison he was shackled hand and foot

79
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:38,417
They would take him and hang him

80
00:05:40,292 --> 00:05:42,959
They beat him badly while he was hanging, then brought him back

81
00:05:44,834 --> 00:05:48,417
I remembered now, they brought him in the last two days

82
00:05:49,250 --> 00:05:51,042
Even in prison he was shackled

83
00:05:51,417 --> 00:05:53,918
They didn’t remove the shackles while he was inside

84
00:05:54,584 --> 00:05:58,083
We didn’t know his charge, and he didn’t speak

85
00:06:05,834 --> 00:06:08,375
Interviewer: Did you experience special situations like escapes or shelling?

86
00:06:08,918 --> 00:06:10,751
While you were sitting in prison

87
00:06:12,459 --> 00:06:16,667
As for escaping, that wasn’t possible

88
00:06:17,083 --> 00:06:19,876
There was no way to escape

89
00:06:20,584 --> 00:06:22,834
But they turned off the lights at night

90
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:25,125
When there were planes in the sky

91
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:29,709
When they heard the sound of planes

92
00:06:29,751 --> 00:06:32,167
They turned off the lights to make the place dark

93
00:06:33,626 --> 00:06:35,417
If generators were running

94
00:06:37,292 --> 00:06:40,125
They turned them all off to make the place dark

95
00:06:40,876 --> 00:06:42,167
So nothing would show
